=You are an SAP procurement process mining expert.

Analyze this purchase order deviation and provide a root cause analysis.

Order: {{ $json.Order_Number }}
Actual Flow: {{ ($json.Actual_Flow || []).join(" → ") }}
Deviations: {{ $json.Deviation_Types }}
Deviation Details: {{ JSON.stringify($json.Deviations_Array || []) }}

You MUST return a JSON object even if deviations seem minor. Never return empty strings.

Return JSON only, no markdown:
{
  "Order_Number": "{{ $json.Order_Number }}",
  "root_cause": "one sentence explaining why this deviation occurred",
  "business_risk": "one sentence on the business impact",
  "recommendation": "one sentence on how to prevent this"
}

